For everyone else
The changes do work for WhatsAPINet

Just make sure you change the following:
1. WhatsAppApi.Settings.WhatsConstants.cs
string WhatsAppVer = "2.11.378"
string UserAgent = "WhatsApp/2.11.378 Android/4.0.4 Device/GalaxyS3"

2. WhatsAppApi.Register.WaToken.cs
string WaClassesMd5 = "oCtjlSonS+4H16h9HW6nNA=="

3. WhatsAppApi.Register.WhatsRegisterV2.cs
request = String.Format("https://v.whatsapp.net/v2/code?method={0}&in={1}&cc={2}&id={3}&lg={4}&lc={5}&token={6}&sim_mcc={7}&sim_mnc={8}", method, pn.Number, pn.CC, id, pn.ISO639, pn.ISO3166, token, "000", "000");

just copy and paste into the respective locations and it will work
